rComments: One of the greatest courses ever taken at U of T, it is hard to believe that there is still such a fan and interesting course offered at this boring university. Materials are pretty challenging as this course deals with advanced game theory topics, thus student should have prior prepartion in ECO204Y/206Y, ECO316H/326H etc. Matthew is so great!

Seriously the best prof I've ever taken in my entire life. Explains everything incredibly well and is extremely enthusiastic. He will answer any question you email him with insane detail and care, no matter how busy he is. You should try to seek out any course taught by this man, you will not regret it.
Teaches Managerial Economics. Is the most animated, high energy class ever. He comes from Pennsylvania State Univ. Final question paper is hard but man, he is brilliant when it comes to teaching!
